Yes. I will close this PR then. The skflow examples have to be adapted to
use the new DNNClassifier and DNNRegressor. If someone wants to do that on
top of this PR it will continue working when the internal code is merged
(hopefully later today). That's one of the major impediments to removing
the TensorFlowDNNEstimator,Regressor classes. As far as I can see at least,
Illia may know more.
